  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Importing investigational medicinal products from approved countries after Brexit
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Importing investigational medicinal products for use in clinical trials if there's a no-deal Brexit.</p>

  </div>
</div>

